==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bú jiàn guāncái bú diàolèi

===Etymology===
Literally: not shed a tear until one sees the coffin
===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[見]][[棺材]][[不]][[掉淚]]'''
# Refuse to be convinced until one is faced with grim reality; cry only when death is staring one in the face; not to accept defeat until at the end of one's rope [tether]; not to shed tears until one sees his own coffin; not to yield until faced with one's own coffin.
===Alternate forms===
[[不见棺材不掉泪]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[留得青山在，不怕沒柴燒]]
*[[不到黃河心不死]]

